1. *Vlasnik* je odgovoran za sve što se dešava u njegovom domu. (The owner is responsible for everything that happens in his house.)

2. On je novi *vlasnik* firme. (He is the new owner of the company.)

3. Ona je postala *vlasnica* njegove naknade. (She became the owner of his compensation.)

4. *Vlasnička* struktura kompanije je promenjena. (The ownership structure of the company has changed.)

5. Njegov roditelj je *vlasnik* nekoliko firmi. (His parent is the owner of several companies.)

6. On je prodat novom *vlasniku*. (He was sold to the new owner.)

7. Svi *vlasnici* imaju pravo glasa. (All owners have the right to vote.)